# Local-only files — never commit

# Author's proper-noun scrub list (gitignored per spec §9.1)
PROPER_NOUN_SCRUB_LIST.md

# Per-project proper-noun list consumed by .githooks/pre-commit
# (Adopter convention documented in CONTRIBUTING.md + docs/getting-started.md)
.cb-scrub-list

# Local environment + secrets
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# OS junk
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Editor configs
.vscode/settings.json
.idea/

# Personal-only wiki notes (per spec §9.3)
.claude/wiki/*-private.md

# Obsidian vault config — created when a .claude/wiki/ is opened as an Obsidian
# vault (see docs/obsidian.md). Churns constantly (workspace.json); never commit.
.obsidian/

# Session handoff artifacts — local-only by design (FAQ option C, adopted Session 6 close)
# The latest handoff is a warm-resume artifact for the next session on this machine; older
# handoffs are git-log history and don't need to travel with the repo. See docs/faq.md §"SESSION_HANDOFF_*.md".
SESSION_HANDOFF_*.md

# Build artifacts (none in v0.1, but reserved)
node_modules/
dist/
build/
*.log

# Local pre-commit hook state
.husky/_/
